HEADWORD: Sea-mail
<hw>Sea"-mail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Sea</ets> +
(perhaps) <ets>Mall</ets> Mally, for <ets>Mary</ets>; hence, Prov. E.
